org.netbeans.spi.debugger.ui

Class ViewFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.netbeans.spi.debugger.ui.ViewFactory

  • public class ViewFactory
extends Object
    Factory that produces debugger views created from registered view models (see Model and it's extension interfaces).
    Since:
    2.34

                                 String helpID,

                                 String toolTip)
        Create TopComponent view from models registered under 'name' path.
        Parameters:
        icon - The icon resource of the TopComponent
        name - Name of the view, under which are the models registered
        helpID - The helpID of the created TopComponent
        propertiesHelpID - The helpID of properties displayed in the view
        displayName - Display name of the view
        toolTip - Tooltip of the view
        Returns:
        TopComponent containing the view created from registered models.

      • createToolTip

        public ToolTipUI createToolTip(String toolTipText,
                               ToolTipUI.Expandable expandable,
                               ToolTipUI.Pinnable pinnable)
        Create a tooltip with additional actions. The tooltip can be expandable to a structured tooltip view, or pinnable as a pin watch.
        Parameters:
        toolTipText - The text to display as a tooltip
        expandable - Description of an expanded tooltip, or null when the tooltip is not expandable
        pinnable - Description of a pin watch created from this tooltip, or null when the tooltip is not pinnable
        Returns:
        A tooltip UI to be shown.
        Since:
        2.54
